metadata.name: h me
metadata.description:
where she exists 
alone
lots of noise in the background
everything intertwines
mind slashes the reality
and she cries
hard to stay focus 
about what is up or not
looking for an escape 
but thinks she can not

maybe through the glowing hole?
or a bad sleep on a wet bank 

to end the day
not the pain

thoughts bounce off the walls of her mind
interaction, she wouldn't mind
but the connection, she is far behind

what is above though, above the glowing light 
wonders she a lot 
a lot more than a crying night
